2	// TDD Test Runner for CSV Report Generator
3	//
4	// This file contains both the library code and the test suite. In .NET 10
5	// file-based apps, top-level statements run first, and type declarations
6	// (records, classes) go at the bottom of the file.
7	//
8	// TDD cycle: tests were conceptually written FIRST to define the API contract,
9	// then the implementation was written to satisfy them (red → green → refactor).
10	// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
